        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <h3><a name="Impact"></a>Impact</h3>

<p>The Flight Search button not responding. Users are unable to select flights, which affects their ability to book travel.</p>

<h3><a name="Expectedbehaviour"></a>Expected behaviour</h3>

<p>The flight selection button should respond when clicked, allowing users to select a flight and proceed with the booking.</p>

<h3><a name="Actualbehaviour"></a>Actual behaviour</h3>

<p>The flight selection button does not respond when clicked. No action occurs, preventing users from selecting flights.</p>

<h3><a name="Stepstoreproduce"></a>Steps to reproduce</h3>

<ul>
	<li>Enter valid From and To locations.</li>
	<li>Select a future travel date.</li>
	<li>Click “Search flights”.</li>
	<li>Clicking search flights button, no navigation happens</li>
</ul>


<h3><a name="Environment"></a>Environment</h3>

<p>N/A</p>

<h3><a name="Workarounds"></a>Workarounds</h3>

<p>N/A</p>

<h3><a name="Otherinformation"></a>Other information</h3>

